{{nihongo|'''''Oshiroi'''''|白粉}} is the powder used for [[skin whitening]], mostly by [[kabuki]] actors and [[geisha]], along with their [[maiko]] apprentices..

"白粉" literally means "white powder", while the pronunciation ''oshiroi'' means "white" (''shiroi'') with the [[Honorific_speech_in_Japanese#Honorific_prefixes|honorific prefix]] ''o-''.

